---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import trainingImg from "../assets/facility.jpg"
---

<section class="training">
    <div class="training__img">
     <Image src={trainingImg} class={"training-img"} alt={"training-image"}/>
    </div>
    <div class="training__texts">
        <h2 class="training__title">It's About Who You Can Become
        </h2>
        <p class="training__paragraph">At our gym, we believe that fitness is more than just physicalâ€”it's about transforming your mindset, pushing your limits, and realizing your full potential. Every workout is a step toward becoming the strongest, healthiest, and most confident version of yourself.</p>
        <p class="training__paragraph">It's not about quick fixes or temporary results; it's about adopting a lifestyle that fuels your passion for self-improvement. With the right mindset and the right support, you can overcome obstacles, break barriers, and achieve goals you never thought possible.
        </p>
        <p class="training__paragraph">Who you become is entirely up to you, but we believe in your potential. With the right training, dedication, and focus, you can turn your goals into reality.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .training{
        padding: 3rem 0rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr);
        justify-content:center;
    }
    .training-img{
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-top-right-radius: 8rem;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 8rem;
    }
    .training__texts{
        background-image: var(--gradient-2);
        padding: 8rem 2rem;
        color: var(--white);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        border-top-left-radius: 8rem;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 8rem;
        
    }
    .training__img{
        width: 100%;
    }
    .training__paragraph{
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        padding-left: 3rem;
    }
    .training__title{
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        padding-left: 3rem;
    }
    @media (max-width:768px ){
        .training{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .training-img{
        border-top-right-radius: 0;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 0;
    }
    .training__texts{
        background-image: var(--gradient-2);
        padding: 5rem 0rem;
        color: var(--white);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        border-top-left-radius: 0;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 0;
    }
    .training__paragraph{
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    .training__title{
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    @media (max-width:540px ){
        .training__title{
            font-size: 2.2rem;
        }
    }
    }
</style>

<script>
            import ScrollReveal from 'scrollreveal';
    const scrollRevealOption = {
  origin: "bottom",
  distance: "50px",
  duration: 1000,
};

ScrollReveal().reveal(".training__title", {
  ...scrollRevealOption,
  origin: "bottom",
});


ScrollReveal().reveal(".training__paragraph", {
  ...scrollRevealOption,
  origin: "bottom",
  delay:500
});
</script>